    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Older vehicle being sold honestly in poor condition and as-is. This is a rough car with heavy cosmetic wear, visible age, and obvious flaws inside and out, so buyers should expect dents, blemishes, tired trim, and a generally worn presentation rather than a clean driver. It may still appeal as a budget project, parts car, or restoration candidate, but it should not be mistaken for a well-sorted example. Priced accordingly for its condition.",
