    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers an affordable way to get behind the wheel without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values practicality, a project opportunity, or inexpensive transportation. Priced with its condition in mind, it represents straightforward value for the right buyer.",
